#

Slow-Cooked Lemon Herb Shrimp and Avocado Soup

$15.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

ShellfishAvocado

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbPaleo

Tags:

SoupSeafoodComfort Food

Description

A vibrant and refreshing soup that combines succulent shrimp with creamy avocado and zesty lemon flavors, perfect for a light yet satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • Large shrimp, peeled and deveined: 1 lb
  • Low-sodium chicken broth: 4 cups
  • Avocado, diced: 1
  • Fresh parsley, chopped: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh dill, chopped: 2 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic, minced: 3 cloves
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
